---
title: Tex-Mex Kidney Bean Quesadillas with Radish Salsa & Chipotle Yoghurt
description: Red kidney beans, Cheddar and carrot unite to make a hearty and delicious filling for these quesadillas. Simply spoon the cheesy filling onto the tortillas, fold them in half and bake. Easy cheesy dinner coming right up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-cannellini-bean-quesadillas-5f8270db.jpg
